name: Alex Johnson
headline: Senior Frontend Developer & UI/UX Enthusiast
summary: Passionate frontend developer with 6+ years of experience building responsive web applications using React, TypeScript, and modern JavaScript frameworks. I love creating intuitive user interfaces that deliver exceptional user experiences. My background includes working with both startups and enterprise companies, giving me a well-rounded perspective on software development.

experience.description: Lead frontend development for enterprise SaaS platform serving 10,000+ users. Architected and implemented a modern React-based dashboard that improved user engagement by 40%. Mentored junior developers and established frontend best practices.

Built responsive web applications using React and Redux for a fast-growing e-commerce startup. Collaborated closely with designers to implement pixel-perfect UI components. Optimized application performance, reducing load times by 60%.

Developed custom websites for small businesses using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Learned responsive design principles and gained experience with various CMS platforms. Contributed to improving the agency's development workflow.

education.degree: Bachelor of Science in Computer Science
